title: Tech baseball off to best start since 1970 with Sunday sweep of Eastern Michigan - Tennessee Tech

description: COOKEVILLE, Tenn. â€“ Solid pitching and another strong offensive showing propelled the Tennessee Tech baseball team to its second straight weekend sweep and a perfect 6-0 start to the year as the Golden Eagles defeated Eastern Michigan, 11-2, Sunday afternoon at Quillen Field and Bush Stadium at the Averitt Express Baseball Complex.
